time complexity: O(n*b^2 + log_b(r) + log_b(l))
space complexity: O(n*b)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Utilizes dynamic programming to pre-calculate counts of numbers with non-decreasing digits for each length up to the length of r, then adjusts counts based on the actual values of l and r.
